OL,3,C'Intergalactic mystery' of how giant
OL,4,Cgalaxies formed close to being solved
OL,6,F"Our findings take us closer to
OL,7,Fsolving a long-standing mystery in
OL,8,Fastronomy that will redefine our
OL,9,Funderstanding of how galaxies were
OL,10,Fcreated in the early universe."
OL,12,FWorking with the Purple Mountain
OL,13,FObservatory in China and the Chinese
OL,14,FAcademy of Science, the team has
OL,15,Fanalysed more than 100 star-forming
OL,16,Fgalaxies in the distant universe using
OL,17,Fthe world's largest radio telescope,
OL,18,Fknown as Alma, in Chile's Atacama
OL,19,Fdesert.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
