OL,3,C'Intergalactic mystery' of how giant
OL,4,Cgalaxies formed close to being solved
OL,6,FStudy lead Dr Qing-Hua Tan, from the
OL,7,FPurple Mountain Observatory, said that
OL,8,Fthe research used a new technique
OL,9,Fwhich looked at the distribution of
OL,10,Flight emitted by distant and highly-
OL,11,Fluminous galaxies.
OL,13,FShe said: "This is the first real
OL,14,Fevidence that spheroids form directly
OL,15,Fthrough intense episodes of star
OL,16,Fformation located in the cores of
OL,17,Fdistant galaxies.
OL,19,F"Astrophysicists have sought to
OL,20,Funderstand this process for decades.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
